<div class="mgWordPara"><div class="WordSection1">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="" xml:lang="EN-US">A
Councillor may have a non-pecuniary interest that they would wish
to disclose.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="" xml:lang=
"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="" xml:lang=
"EN-US">Examples of this may include:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="" xml:lang=
"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt">
<span style="font-family:Symbol"><span style=
"">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span>
<span style="">A member declaring that they have received
correspondence from an applicant/objector in the past. This can be
about the application, but the Member confirms that they have an
open mind during consideration of the item.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt">
<span style="font-family:Symbol"><span style=
"">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span>
<span style="">A Member declaring that they have attended a public
meeting on the application but have an open mind during
consideration of the item.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt">
<span style="font-family:Symbol"><span style=
"">&middot;<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span>
<span style="">A Member is acquainted with the applicant but that
this association would not influence their decision.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="" xml:lang=
"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="" xml:lang=
"EN-US">Members declaring any other interests are not required to
withdraw from the debate and these declarations are made only to
ensure transparency during the <span class="GramE">decision
making</span> process.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div> 
<p class="mgSubItemTitleTxt">Minutes:</p>
